title: HOUR 1- Chris Haynes Oct 08, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 1- Chris Haynes Oct 08, 2020
description:
Chris Haynes tells Dan that Lebron is the MVP although Anthony Davis really does deserve it too. Chris Says that the committee MVP voters are an odd number to prevent a tie. Chris tells Dan that it would be hard for him to vote for a player on the losing team like Jimmy Butler.
